{"ID":270307, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"307\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs306.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs308.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 307<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Righteous Judgments<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Brother Joseph then addressed the Twelve, and said that in all our counsels, especially while\n  on trial of any one, we should see and observe all things appertaining to the subject, and discern the\n  spirit<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> by which either party was governed. We should be in a situation to understand every spirit\n  and judge righteous judgment<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> and not be asleep.<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> We should keep order and not let the council be\n  imposed upon by unruly conduct.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> The Saints need not think because I am familiar with them and\n  am playful and cheerful, that I am ignorant of what is going on.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> Iniquity of any kind cannot be\n  sustained in the Church,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and it will not fare well where I am; for I am determined while I do lead\n  the Church, to lead it right.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> (May 27, 1843.) DHC 5:411.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Testimony Concerning Brigham Young and H. C. Kimball<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Of the Twelve Apostles chosen in Kirtland, and ordained under the hands of Oliver Cowdery,\n  David Whitmer and myself,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> there have been but two<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> but what have lifted their heel against\n  me<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span>&mdash;namely Brigham Young and Heber C. Kimball. (May 28, 1843.) DHC 5:412.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Purpose of the Gathering of Israel<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">A large assembly of the Saints met at the Temple stand. Hymn by the choir. Prayer by Elder\n  Parley P. Pratt, and singing.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">President Joseph Smith remarked&mdash;&ldquo;I am a rough stone. The sound of the hammer and chisel\n  was never heard on me until the Lord took me in hand. I desire the learning and wisdom of heaven\n  alone.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> I have not the least idea, if Christ should come to the earth and preach such rough things as\n  He preached to the Jews, but that this generation would reject Him<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> for being so rough.&rdquo;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">He then took for his text the 37th verse of 23rd chapter of Matthew&mdash;&ldquo;O Jerusalem, Jerusalem,\n  thou that killest the prophets and stonest them which are sent unto thee; how often would I have\n  gathered thy children together, even as a hen gathereth her chickens under her wings, and ye would\n  not.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">This subject was presented to me since I came to the stand. What was the object of gathering\n  the Jews, or the people of<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109528\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109528)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109528)\">1 Cor. 12:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110147\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110147)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110147)\">Heb. 4:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108713\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108713)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108713)\">John 7:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109948\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109948)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109948)\">1 Thes. 5:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113628\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113628)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113628)\">D&amp;C 35:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116530\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116530)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116530)\">D&amp;C 134:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109636\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109636)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109636)\">2 Cor. 2:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111681\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111681)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111681)\">Mosiah 19:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111721\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111721)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111721)\">Mosiah 26:36<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112944\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112944)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112944)\">Moro. 6:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113079\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113079)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113079)\">D&amp;C 1:31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113386\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113386)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113386)\">D&amp;C 20:54<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109484\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109484)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109484)\">1 Cor. 9:16-18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113271\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113271)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113271)\">D&amp;C 18:37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107697\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107697)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107697)\">Zech. 4:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106713\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106713)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106713)\">Ps. 41:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108778\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108778)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108778)\">John 13:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115751\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115751)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115751)\">D&amp;C 121:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114379\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114379)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114379)\">D&amp;C 76:5-10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116965\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116965)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116965)\">Abr. 1:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114871\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114871)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114871)\">D&amp;C 88:75,85<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108190\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108190)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108190)\">Matt. 23:37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}